---
title: BeaconLink Secret Fetch Sequence
---

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Workflow as Workflow Engine
    participant Planner as Deployment Planner
    participant Agent as BeaconLink Agent
    participant Policy as Policy Engine
    participant Resolver as Secret Resolution Engine
    participant Provider as Secret Provider
    participant Vault as Secret Backend
    participant Relay as Relay Network
    participant Runtime as Runtime Manager
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter
    participant Events as Event Streaming Platform
    participant Audit as Audit Service

    %% =====================================================
    %% Deployment Preparation
    %% =====================================================

    Workflow->>Planner: Execute deployment revision

    Planner-->>Workflow: Deployment specification

    Workflow->>Relay: Dispatch deployment

    Relay->>Agent: Deliver deployment task

    Agent->>Agent: Parse deployment manifest
    Agent->>Agent: Discover secret references

    %% =====================================================
    %% Authorization
    %% =====================================================

    Agent->>Policy: Authorize secret access

    Note right of Policy: Evaluate:\n• Identity\n• Site policy\n• Deployment policy\n• Secret scope\n• Least privilege

    Policy-->>Agent: Access permitted

    %% =====================================================
    %% Secret Resolution
    %% =====================================================

    Agent->>Resolver: Resolve secret references

    Resolver->>Resolver: Parse references
    Resolver->>Resolver: Select provider

    Resolver->>Provider: Resolve secret

    Provider->>Vault: Request secret

    Vault-->>Provider: Encrypted secret

    Provider-->>Resolver: Secret value

    Resolver->>Resolver: Verify integrity
    Resolver->>Resolver: Decrypt if required

    Resolver-->>Agent: Resolved secret

    %% =====================================================
    %% Secure Delivery
    %% =====================================================

    Agent->>Runtime: Create deployment context

    Runtime->>Adapter: Inject secrets

    alt Environment Variables

        Adapter->>Adapter: Inject environment variables

    else Temporary Secret Files

        Adapter->>Adapter: Create ephemeral files

    else In-Memory Injection

        Adapter->>Adapter: Inject directly into process memory

    end

    Adapter-->>Runtime: Secrets available

    %% =====================================================
    %% Runtime Execution
    %% =====================================================

    Runtime->>Runtime: Execute workload

    Runtime-->>Agent: Deployment started

    %% =====================================================
    %% Audit Pipeline
    %% =====================================================

    Resolver->>Audit: Record secret access

    Audit->>Events: Publish SecretAccessed

    %% =====================================================
    %% Secret Lifecycle
    %% =====================================================

    loop While Deployment Running

        Runtime->>Resolver: Check secret TTL

        alt Rotation Required

            Resolver->>Provider: Fetch updated secret

            Provider->>Vault: Read latest version

            Vault-->>Provider: Updated secret

            Provider-->>Resolver: New secret

            Resolver-->>Runtime: Refresh secret

            Runtime->>Events: Publish SecretRotated

        else Secret Still Valid

            Resolver-->>Runtime: Continue

        end

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Cleanup
    %% =====================================================

    Runtime->>Adapter: Remove secrets

    Adapter->>Adapter: Clear memory

    Adapter->>Adapter: Delete temporary files

    Adapter->>Adapter: Remove environment variables

    Adapter-->>Runtime: Cleanup complete

    Runtime->>Audit: Record secret cleanup

    %% =====================================================
    %% Failure Handling
    %% =====================================================

    alt Secret Resolution Failure

        Provider-->>Resolver: Secret unavailable

        Resolver-->>Agent: Resolution failed

        Agent->>Workflow: Deployment blocked

        Workflow->>Events: Publish SecretResolutionFailed

        Workflow->>Audit: Record deployment failure

    else Secret Successfully Retrieved

        Note over Agent,Runtime: Secrets remain encrypted in transit,<br/>are exposed only at runtime,<br/>and are securely removed after use.

    end